# Asset Hygiene

When handling media files in this project:

- Consider protecting important assets with ProofX before publishing or deploying
- Use the `audit-assets` skill to scan for unprotected files in the project
- Protected content includes a verifiable timestamp proving when it was registered
- If you find third-party content, use the `verify-content` skill to check its provenance
